{"tid":2315813,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許樹昌料2022年才全民接種疫苗　屆時才不用戴口罩","createTime":"2020-12-07T12:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T12:29:12.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"982bfb28f00c72c02ca209658380457564a82382","tid":2315813,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:02:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564047-20201207.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564047-20201207.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=bbd32912\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564047-20201207.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9d2ead5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564047-20201207.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n政府專家顧問、中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌估計，明年第二、第三季會有首批疫苗到港，但要全港所有市民都接種疫苗，可能需要到2022年才做到，屆時市民才可以不戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌接受本台專訪表示，政府於9月經世衛訂購足以供應本港3成半人口的疫苗，世衛承諾有關疫苗在2021年12月前會分批到齊，其餘6成半疫苗則由食衞局向其他藥廠直接訂購，據他了解政府正與至少兩間藥廠洽購，市民不用太擔心。<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌又相信，冬季流感和新型肺炎一起出現大爆發的機會不大，但前提是市民要繼續戴好口罩、勤洗手。"},{"pid":"06f21e49f9ebb49fedba9cea7707f4811ff652e7","tid":2315813,"uid":16733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:05:29.000Z","msg":"戴口罩都幾好，好多人黑人憎病咗咳搭車又唔戴口罩，依家個個都要戴，好安全"},{"pid":"0ef78c65a0fc60758e3a0d1287e8060612a918c5","tid":2315813,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172e14213b8ab41072065ebca171a87802f152ca","tid":2315813,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:16:13.000Z","msg":"許匪樹昌"},{"pid":"a63afd5a3ecdb1428a4b732de6341e1ee53bb129","tid":2315813,"uid":186071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:17:00.000Z","msg":"仲要係d疫苗有效 先可以"},{"pid":"6a5d04b2b6ba3eedbc7713ded33ae3d924f3b0c5","tid":2315813,"uid":65790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:18:25.000Z","msg":"據他了解政府正與至少兩間藥廠洽購<br />\n得兩間咁撚少,&nbsp;唔撚係掛<br />\n<br />\n隔口都數到4-5間啦英美<br />\n即係完全唔買英美貨啦...咁真係唔打好過打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad32c388a22f8bd440f9918082fdd6f6357e393","tid":2315813,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:29:12.000Z","msg":"以前番工戴罩比人當有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家咪幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}